      <!-- First section of info -->
      <h2>we are conscious.</h2>
      <p>
        Conscious. is a collaborative exhibition that aims to raise awareness. That's it.
         The exhibition features artworks from three artists, each of whom have created a
        collection of artworks that explore the theme of awareness, mindfulness and
        wellbeing. The exhibition is a celebration of the arts and the
        therapeutic benefits of artistic expression.
     
        <img src="images/portfolio-project1.jpg" alt="Portfolio Project 1">
        <img src="images/portfolio-project2.jpg" alt="Portfolio Project 2">
