      <!-- Second section of info -->
      <h2>meet the hands and hearts behind Conscious.</h2>
      <p>
      <h3>Becca</h3>
      <p>
        Becca is an artist, writer and designer based in Malta, currently finishing her Bachelor's in Digital Arts at the University of Malta. 
        Her work explores themes of mindfulness, consciousness and the human condition.
        Becca hates the colour orange and her favourite book is Notes from Under the Floorboards by Fyodor Dostoevsky.
      </p>
      <!-- Add content showcasing artworks in the gallery -->
      <img src="images/portfolio-project1.jpg" alt="Portfolio Project 1">
