        <h3>Anna</h3>
        <p>
          Anna Chiara is a Bachelor's student of Digital Arts at the University of Malta.
          Born on the 16th August of 2002 in Italy, she has showcased her best photographs in this exhibition. 
          Anna specializes in illustration but still enjoys taking photographs of her journeys around the world, depicting the most striking subjects of her travels.
        </p>
